{"tid":2158062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特首通知行會刪利益登記冊上有關劍橋名譽院士身份","createTime":"2020-08-15T12:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:03:03.000Z","uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a64ff68c4a70f4b1e3362d15903c475e23863b04","tid":2158062,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"行政會議秘書處按特首林鄭月娥通知，刪除她在個人利益登記冊上，有關英國劍橋大學沃爾森學院名譽院士身份的項目。<br />\n<br />\n該學院的院長上月曾發表聲明，表示學院強烈支持保障學院所有成員的人權及言論自由，並對香港實施《港區國安法》後發生的事件深感關注，學院會檢視林鄭月娥的榮譽院士資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543928-20200815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543928-20200815.htm&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=be0355e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543928-20200815.htm&h=d0560cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543928-20200815.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0d9c46a8daca42658f5584b9df1436f552a68e76","tid":2158062,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"而家係我飛你，唔係你飛我。"}]}